title: Are The Democrats Trying To Interfere In Another Election? (Ep 1751)
description:
In this episode, I address the question, “are the Democrat’s planning to interfere in the 2022 election?” 

News Picks:

Terror at the border?

The clearest example yet of the superiority of conservative economic policies.

Elon can make these three moves to counter the Twitter board.

Florida’s anti-grooming bill has public support.


Libs are demanding airlines impose their own mask mandates.


Libs lose their marbles over the loss of the mask mandate.
